<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Van dak tum-un! tuni'n kipahna a um,
 Mikhat gitloh apat a hung kit;
 En in! Pa'n lampi-ah ana lamtuoh hi,
 A Cha gimthei, vakmang a na lawp.

[V2]
 Lopi! Lopi! Angelte la sak!
 Lopi takin kingkang ngeih tumin;
 Tatsate'n la a sau, tuipi luong bangin,
 Suohchakna thu lopi la'n a sau.

[V3]
 2. Van dak tum-un! tuni'n kipahna a um,
 Vakmang chu tu'n lawp kit ahi tai;
 Gitlohna lampi apat hukdam ei tai;
 Tatdawk leh piengthak ahung hitai.

[V4]
 3. Van dak tum-un! tuni'n guolvakna bawlun,
 Angelte'n zawh la kipah um sau;
 Thu kipah um gen unla, gen sawn zel un,
 Thagau lul tak a pienthak ziekin.</lyrics>
<title>RINGTHE BELS OF HEAVEN</title>
</song>